Metadata: This is one in a series of 10 signs posted along the bay front in Newport, Oregon. The "Newport's Commercial Fisheries" series includes: Salmon Troller, Tuna Troller, Bottom Trawler, Dungeness Crab, Hagfish, Longliner, Pacific Whiting Midwater Trawler, Shrimp Trawler, Sablefish Traps, and Newport's Commercial Fishing Community.
